#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:3
#: 25f1b1d4c35a415480ee09cc2ff7a827
msgid "How to upgrade to Qubes 4.1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:6
#: 57c2625830b44887a3b78a740a97df07
msgid ""
"This page explains how to upgrade from Qubes 4.0 to Qubes 4.1. There are two"
" ways to upgrade: a clean installation or an in-place upgrade. In general, a"
" clean installation is simpler and less error-prone, but an in-place upgrade"
" allows you to preserve your customizations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:9
#: 1ffe99ca338647a7bbaf6f2013732012
msgid "Back up"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:12
#: e597b307cbdd4665aeb44a703c826070
msgid ""
"Before attempting either an in-place upgrade or a clean installation, we "
"strongly recommend that you first :doc:`back up your system </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` so that you don’t lose any data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:15
#: 90f68fcff570457eb738fbb09c97ae63
msgid "Clean installation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:18
#: 0871ff272ba1436799c6f0609ddc98ca
msgid ""
"If you would prefer to perform a clean installation rather than upgrading "
"in-place:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:20
#: 12891519943245a2bd5e2e0f0ce64685
msgid ""
"Create a :ref:`backup <user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-"
"migrate:creating a backup>` of your current installation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:22
#: 079283e076ca455eb463fa3cfc9859f3
msgid ""
"`Download <https://www.qubes-os.org/downloads/>`__ the latest 4.1 release."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:24
#: b21827e6da8343d88e0131060d552004
msgid ""
"Follow the :doc:`installation guide </user/downloading-installing-"
"upgrading/installation-guide>` to install Qubes 4.1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:26
#: 9e02e31736ad41b68b99b43440212745
msgid ""
":ref:`Restore from your backup <user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-"
"and-migrate:restoring from a backup>` on your new 4.1 installation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:31
#: 7828ce30129c4b2782927fdc0f70da73
msgid "In-place upgrade"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:34
#: 62ee893397714d85ab44b4534f19fbd4
msgid ""
"**Warning:** It is not possible to upgrade directly from releases earlier "
"than 4.0. If you’re still on an earlier release, please either perform a "
"`clean installation of 4.1 <#clean-installation>`__ or :doc:`upgrade to 4.0 "
"</user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_0>` first."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:36
#: e52dfda9e84e47ecbf83f10c423b9cf6
msgid ""
"The upgrade may take several hours, and will download several gigabytes of "
"data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:38
#: 7a229ff81dd0474c9b59c49581020395
msgid ""
"In place upgrade is a complex operation. For this reason, we provide a "
"``qubes-dist-upgrade`` tool to handle all the necessary steps automatically."
" You can install it with the following command in the dom0 terminal:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:46
#: 71b76e1838c845e28c008ca881cd9d62
msgid ""
"The upgrade consists of seven stages — six before restarting the system — "
"labeled “STAGE 0” through “STAGE 5” in the options list below. The seventh "
"stage is rebuilding the application and features lists, which you can start "
"with the ``--resync-appmenus-features`` option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:48
#: 7d54555ddb064317a2edbda2223ecb99
msgid ""
"Full list of options can be obtained with ``qubes-dist-upgrade --help``:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:83
#: 9dab4f6b624e45599d62ef3009252d5b
msgid "After installing the tool, upgrade can be performed all at once with:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:91
#: b999aee78ae44aea980efde6e2c84ef2
msgid ""
"Optionally, an ``--assumeyes`` (or ``-y``) option can be used to "
"automatically accept all the actions without confirmation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:93
#: 08b848a30a8442aea91e9c1d7f64f1ea
msgid ""
"Alternatively, each upgrade stage can be started separately (see the list of"
" options above)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:95
#: bc5f16072f3c4fafba1f3d3376f72bff
msgid ""
"After completing “STAGE 0” through “STAGE 5”, restart the system. Then "
"perform the final step:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:103
#: 9081cd8da727460ea6b313721bae4d69
msgid "When this completes, you can start using Qubes OS 4.1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:106
#: 3b8a7200a0a44e7eb345d705ddfe2126
msgid "Known issues"
msgstr "Bekannte Probleme"

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:109
#: 6a949b56978445ef8f210c336edfbca0
msgid ""
"The script does not convert LUKS1 to LUKS2 disk encryption format (fresh "
"Qubes 4.1 install uses LUKS2 for disk encryption, while earlier versions use"
" LUKS1)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:111
#: 5b6fb4af406b43ef9e8fe40c1766ec78
msgid ""
"Early Qubes 4.0 pre-releases (before R4.0-rc2) made ``/boot/efi`` partition "
"only 200MB, which is too small for R4.1. In case of such partition layout, "
"clean installation is necessary."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:113
#: 9ece769d14e144c6a4bbff5ff8de837a
msgid ""
"If user has created some custom qrexec policy entries, they may not be "
"correctly handled in R4.1, resulting in denying all the calls. It is advised"
" to verify if there are not qrexec policy errors in the log after the system"
" restart - using ``journalctl -b`` command."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:117
#: 4458593ca1d246a493b5546dbc7b38d0
msgid ""
"If any early upgrade stage fails, the ``qubes-dist-upgrade`` tool will try "
"to restore previous system state. After fixing an issue, the tool can be "
"started again, to retry the operation. If a later stage (number 3 or later) "
"fails, the tool may not be able to rollback the changes. But it may still be"
" possible to retry the upgrade."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:120
#: 043c9d6a9dac4a22bec646deb2b6afca
msgid "Update"
msgstr "Aktualisieren"

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1.rst:123
#: 4efef65f6cf143788bb96e35120461a9
msgid ""
"After upgrading or performing a clean installation, we strongly recommend "
":doc:`updating your system </user/how-to-guides/how-to-update>`."
msgstr ""
